This standard specifies the technical requirements, inspection rules and labels for personal fall protection systems. ;
It is applicable for the personal fall protection systems used by users with the sum of body weight and loading less than 100kg in high altitude work, climb and suspension working.  ;
This standard is not applicable for the personal fall protection systems used in athletic sports and fire fighting. ;

This standard specifies the technical requirements, test methods, inspection rules and labelling for static protective clothing. ;
It is applicable for static protective clothing to be used in situations which may possibly cause hazards of electric shock, fire and explosion.  ;
The static protective clothing defined in this standard is not applicable for resisting main voltages. ;
